Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========OP==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:11.38,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是连前进轨道都无法改变的几率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:15.88,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟、被「命运」所束缚的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:26.39,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要将它重写、因为若能看见你和未来 不是最棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧！我只想在战斗中成长 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,击穿阴天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.53,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍旧熊熊燃烧 雷鸣撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:37.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除梦魇 看见未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:39.87,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,过去、未来、还有如今当下、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏惧过去 现在为了被托付的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的骄傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:50.88,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想看到眼泪、所以要不断嘶吼！一直永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:54.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会堕落！因为扬起的风会让我凌驾于命运之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:02:01.22,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为身后、有着想要守护的笑容！ 永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,为了彼此！我会揍飞你心中的痛苦！让悲伤什么的永远安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.85,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}无论多少次…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:34.87,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光摇曳 我们未来的蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:42.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会实现 描绘明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:46.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不会磨灭 铭记在心中的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:55.72,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是无尽的泪水能掩盖伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:04.77,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无需畏惧 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:13.24,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向着无边无际的天空 张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:19.08,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那轮皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:24.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲伤 也要怀着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算无法回头 也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:35.89,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的梦想 闪耀在探索的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:41.89,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最宝贵的那份思念 仍旧在延续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:47.73,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪里 我们都一起走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:55.53,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心灵之匙吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Avant==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7头龙从日蚀的大门中走出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7位灭龙魔法师与龙开始战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在拉开序幕的是 龙的时代
Comment: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,==========Main==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.47,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(524,0)\pos(646,520)}人对人、龙对龙、人对龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大块头 别小看了雷神众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你也是生物 就一定会感受到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗文字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精机枪 妖精群舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重粒子阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷龙的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 吃了这么多招的感觉不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用 没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之狱炎会将魔法燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 真是笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让拉克萨斯对付它还真是不适合啊 火和雷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有水之灭龙魔法师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火的话这里倒是有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了哦 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下去吧 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到你了 炎之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 汝是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是夏 我现在要把你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事谁都不会想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了要吃掉你就会吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美味的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 你这家伙打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…就…交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去城堡那边 拉克萨斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去帮助温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 温蒂虽然是灭龙魔法师 但还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有她一个人的话 会很吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉克萨斯 我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之龙 就交给炎之灭龙魔法师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那家伙交给你没有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我要把这家伙吃掉提升我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们去城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休要激怒吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要吞掉吾之火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类大言不惭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此等感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是此等感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙王 伊古尼鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟…和伊古尼鲁是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道伊古尼鲁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之友人 亦是火龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼鲁是我的老爹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 这究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是未来的我的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看别人的日记 还真是个好兴趣啊 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 顺便看一下我的调教日记怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是无视我吗 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是龙的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的破坏力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这个力量 就一定能杀掉阿库诺罗基亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后由我来支配这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎裂吧 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃烧吧 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消逝吧 生命的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是龙之王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于龙王祭诞生的新生之王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影将在这里成为光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为绝对之光 照亮世间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不需要这种肮脏不堪的光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的光存在于我们自己心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你那微弱的光 根本就什么都找不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么夏会骑在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特拉斯费雷姆 你背叛了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾只顺从吾心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼鲁之子 便是我友人之子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特拉斯费雷姆 你背叛了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾只顺从吾心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊古尼鲁之子 便是我友人之子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的操龙魔法居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我的意识被魔法阻断了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是成为了朋友而已 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然说…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 从背后绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莎古雷亚 小心背后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮无法撼动吾之火焰之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰无法摧毁我的金钢之躯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休要小觑吾之狱炎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱中喷涌而出的巨人之焰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 吃掉了巨人之焰的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾之友人的龙之炎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然…吃掉了阿特拉斯费雷姆的火焰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙和龙在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好厉害 但为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经美丽的花之都如今鲜血四溅 一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与龙与魔的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙与龙战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与龙战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是古代的灾厄 龙王祭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无…无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都无法复原了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆造型 冰冻的黑雷之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂乱的风牙之社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种数量 这种威压感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在于我的记忆中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰双剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了你的这个招数 还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那我就不客气地使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 特洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有蕾比 我们也是车道·引擎小队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隼天翔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物乱舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能上啊 特洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫色之焰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父子的火焰攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 我也不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的烟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了 怪物们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中的还要不服老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷神的荷电粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这是第几只了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩铁壁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸠拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为敌人是很棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作为同伴 没有人比他更可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龙的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就封住你的行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西根本没效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真攻击的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龙的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就行了吧 罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是赢不了龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们被命令只是不能杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是另一个可能性的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既是你的影子 也是你心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 闭嘴 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实呆着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个绝望的世界里 只有你能幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 成为王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 我不想成为王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是听谁的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是你自己吗 罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤了我们龙 想要成为世界之王的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是七年后的你的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受吧 你的心将会被黑暗侵染
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是今后必定会被侵染吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运只能接受 你不会死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间回溯 一个小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西…呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自称罗格…七年后的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是另一个未来人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把露西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格看来成长为了厉害的魔法师了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说是未来就有弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉这个时代的罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来罗格的存在也会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 根据时间悖论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来罗格存在着 也即证明过去的罗格绝对不会被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是时间正常流转的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在时间混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来露西以及知晓时间混乱的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都变成了打破正常的虚数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉现在的罗格 未来的罗格会被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来罗格被消灭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里的露西也许也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来罗格由我来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一味凭意气用事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来罗格是在哪里走错了路 他不是现在的罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的罗格没有任何罪孽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要将他杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也要走错路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会对现在的罗格出手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 已经束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格变成了这次事件的整体关键
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 罗格没有从未来过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门不会被打开 龙也不会来袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让世界复原 必须杀死罗格
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Preview==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 大叔的火真心好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 龙的火果然比一般货要好吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你问的还真好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话题要说起来就长了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙之炎的高品质简直让我神魂颠倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你所谓的说来话长么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长年酿成的醇香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.80,0:24:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像开启了一个很奇怪的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 罪孽与牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 大叔火焰的风味就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 后续我下次再听好了
